federal prosecutors urged the jury in the fawaz 
younis sky piracy trial to find the defendant guilty and to reject 
his claim that he led the hijacking of a plane from beirut in 1985 
on orders from the lebanese militia to which he belonged 
hijacking said prosecutor karen morrissette is a violation of 
