the cost of employing women in management is greater than the 
cost of employing men ms schwartz wrote in the reviews 
januaryfebruary issue in her article management women and the 
new facts of life 
this is a jarring statement partly because it is true but 
mostly because it is something people are reluctant to talk about 
she wrote 
published by harvard business school the review has 210000 
