industrial and consumer products emhart also provides electronic 
systems technology sevices for commercial markets and the government 
the board was advised that the nature of the offer the rumors 
and the unusual trading activity that preceded the offer and 
toppers financing arrangements for the offer raise serious legal 
questions scott said in his letter to shareholders 
emharts stock was at 3275 a share when topper tendered its 
offer the stock had risen almost 10 a share in the month prior to 
the offer amid takeover rumors 
scott added in a prepared statement i have grave concerns 
about the abnormal trading activity that occurred in emharts stock 
before the announcement of the topper offer this trading raises 
disquieting questions as to whether the governments actions aimed 
