the measure approved by the labor standards subcommittee was 
virtually identical to legislation the senate labor and human 
resources passed wednesday and advanced democratic plans to take the 
first hike in the minimum since 1981 to the floors of both houses 
within two weeks 
both bills would raise the minimum in increments over three 
years to 465 an hour by 1991 
